The paper deals with object proposals for text recognition, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves text detection and recognition, which are topics in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed method uses a similarity-based region grouping algorithm, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
